A production-ready Android app scaffolded by the OmniSight SKILL-ANDROID
(P8 #293) pilot pack. Built on Jetpack Compose + Kotlin 2.0 with first-
party FCM push and Play Billing integration wired out of the box.

Features:
- Material 3 dynamic-color UI on Android 12+
- Edge-to-edge Compose layouts on all supported API levels
- Server-verified Play Billing purchases (never grants entitlements on
  raw client responses)
- SHA-256 fingerprint logging for FCM tokens (never logs raw tokens)
- Accessibility-first — content descriptions on every interactive control
